sentence: show me all flights from san diego to phoenix on a boeing seven thirty seven
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.aircraft_code_sequence||'"', '"'||v6.aircraft_code||'"',
 '"'||v6.manufacturer||'"', '"'||v6.basic_type||'"' FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2, airport_service v3,
 city v4, equipment_sequence v5, aircraft v6 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'SAN DIEGO'))) AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'PHOENIX'))) AND ((v0.aircraft_code_sequence = ANY v5.aircraft_code_sequence) 
AND ((v5.aircraft_code = ANY v6.aircraft_code) AND ((v6.manufacturer = 'BOEING') 
AND (v6.basic_type = '737'))))));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' SAN DIEGO ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' PHOENIX ' ) ) AND FLIGHT . AIRCRAFT_CODE_SEQUENCE IN ( SELECT EQUIPMENT_SEQUENCE . AIRCRAFT_CODE_SEQUENCE FROM EQUIPMENT_SEQUENCE WHERE EQUIPMENT_SEQUENCE . AIRCRAFT_CODE IN ( SELECT AIRCRAFT . AIRCRAFT_CODE FROM AIRCRAFT WHERE ( AIRCRAFT.MANUFACTURER = ' BOEING ' AND AIRCRAFT.BASIC_TYPE = ' 737 ' ) ) ) ) ) ) ;
